    #fullpage
      section.vertical-scrolling
        header.site-header
          .container.text-center
            .row
              .col-md-12.visible-inline-block
                h1
                  a(href='/') nodeschool costa rica
            .row
              .col-md-12.visible-inline-block
                br
                p.lead - aprende javascript y node.js -
